# 🌐 Landing Page Project

This is a simple landing page project built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It includes a basic modal form to collect user information and improve interaction on the page.

## 🚀 Features

- Responsive layout
- Modal contact form
- Basic form validation
- Simple UI interactions with JavaScript
- Clean and minimal design

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

## 📌 Status

This project is currently in development. More features and improvements will be added over time.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project is part of my learning process in web development and helps me improve my frontend skills and UI design practice.

